  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à GNOME Games</title>
    <para>
      The <application>GNOME Games</application> is a collection
      of simple, but addictive games from the
      <application>GNOME</application> Desktop project.
      They represent many of the popular games et include card games,
      puzzle games et arcade games.
    </para>
    &lfs72_checked;
